headline.main: THE ITALIAN PLANES; No Match for Hurricanes

lead_paragraph: The Italians, apparently, commenced to put serious military pressure on Greece yesterday, using their bombing planes for the first time in repeated though rather small-scale raids on Salonika and Piraeus.
